metadata.title: Happy Anniversary Paper Presents for Him, Anniversary Presents for Couple, Printed Gag Toilet Paper Present
features: Best Anniversary or Valentine's Day present for him or her.
Fun and romantic gift for your anniversary. It reads "Happy Anniversary, I Love You".
Nothing says “I Love You” like the gift of romantic toilet paper.
One roll of toilet paper. They are 3 ply soft quality anniversary toilet paper. Fits any standard size toilet roll holder.
Great gift for men or women, husband or wife, boyfriend, girlfriend or spouse.
description: The anniversary toilet paper top sheet and reads "Happy Anniversary, I Love You". The intended use is to get a big laugh! The best way to get a laugh is to switch out the TP the night before and let the recipient be surprised upon his/her visit to the bathroom in the morning. This is as a romantic gift delivered to the recipient. Our funny and romantic anniversary toilet paper is printed on 3-ply TP.  The toilet paper is also usable for the normal TP use.  Tip: 1 roll of toilet paper per order.
